.TH CPPTEST 1 "March 2026" "5.0" "CppTest Manual"
.SH NAME
cpptest \- Advanced competitive programming testing utility
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B cpptest
[\fIOPTIONS\fR] [\fIFILE\fR] [\fIDIRECTORY\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Automated testing tool for C++. Supports test generation, stress testing, isolation, memory profiling, interactive mode, custom checkers, clang-tidy, and multiple compilers.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-I ", " \-\-interactive
\fBInteractive Mode.\fR Compiles the solution and runs it in the terminal, allowing you to provide manual input via keyboard. Disables automated testing.
.TP
.BR \-S ", " \-\-stress
\fBStress Mode.\fR Requires \fIslow.cpp\fR and \fIgen.cpp\fR. Runs an infinite loop comparing the output of your solution against the brute-force solution. Uses \fIcheck.cpp\fR if available.
.TP
.BR \-R ", " \-\-no-comments
\fBRemove Comments.\fR \fBWARNING:\fR Permanently removes comments from \fImain.cpp\fR and exits immediately.
.TP
.BR \-F ", " \-\-fix
\fBAuto-Fix Mode.\fR Automatically applies style fixes (clang-format, clang-tidy) to the source code and exits immediately.
.TP
.BR \-a ", " \-\-manual
\fBManual Tests Only.\fR Run tests found in the current directory and \fItests/\fR folder.
.TP
.BR \-g ", " \-\-generated
\fBGenerated Tests Only.\fR Run tests found in \fIgen_tests/\fR folder only.
.TP
.BR \-n ", " \-\-no-gen
\fBNo Generation.\fR Skip running the generator, even if \fIgen.cpp\fR is present.
.TP
.BR \-G ", " \-\-gen-only
\fBGenerate & Exit.\fR Compiles \fIgen.cpp\fR, generates tests into \fIgen_tests/\fR, and exits.
.TP
.BR \-i ", " \-\-in-place
Run tests directly in the source directory.
.TP
.BR \-f ", " \-\-fast
Skip static analysis (clang-tidy/format).
.TP
.BR \-K ", " \-\-force-checker
Force usage of \fIcheck.cpp\fR.
.TP
.BR \-k ", " \-\-force-diff
Force usage of standard diff.
.TP
.BR \-p ", " \-\-prompt
Copy the standard AI prompt (for regular CP problems) directly to the system clipboard.
.TP
.BR \-P ", " \-\-prompt-interactive
Copy the interactive AI prompt (for problems requiring an interactor) directly to the system clipboard.
.TP
.BR \-u ", " \-\-update
Self-update from GitHub.
.TP
.BR \-w ", " \-\-no-errors
Disable Warnings as Errors. Compile without treating warnings as errors (-Werror).
.TP
.BR \-v ", " \-\-version
Show Version. Display the version of cpptest and exit.
.TP
.BR \-c ", " \-\-tidy
Show Tidy Path. Display the path to the .clang-tidy file being used (searches current and parent directories) and exit.
.SH MEMORY PROFILING
If \fI/usr/bin/time\fR is available on the system, cpptest will automatically measure and display the peak resident set size (RAM usage) for each test case in MB.
.SH COLORED DIFF
If standard output comparison fails, cpptest utilizes \fIgit diff --word-diff\fR to highlight the exact mismatched characters in the terminal.
.SH AUTHOR
MootSasa
